<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.1.8">
<l>koṅkaivaṉ kūṉicoṟ koṇṭu kuvalayat</l>
<l>tuṅkak kariyum pariyu mirācciyamu</l>
<l>meṅkum parataṟ karuḷivaṉ kāṉaṭai</l>
<l>yaṅkaṇṇa ṉappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟā</l>
<l rend="indent">ṉammaṉē yappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With the word of her with the hard hunch-back</l>
<l rend="indent">[that swells like] breasts,</l>
<l>having granted the tallest elephants upon the earth,</l>
<l>horses, and [his] kingdom in all directions to Bharata,</l>
<l>[and] settling in the harsh jungle,</l>
<l>He with beautiful eyes is making [the face of] a hobgoblin.</l>
<l>Oh! He is making [the face of] a hobgoblin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
